  "texts": [
    "Developing self-understanding and situation analysis are outcomes of mental cognition through reflection.",
    "1 This allows the individual to learn from one's personal experiences while utilizing critical thinking to reach a deeper level of learning.",
    "2, 3 According to constructivism theory, changing concepts is a direct result of the way one constructs the acquired knowledge and one's interpretation of a certain event.",
    "4 In medical education, reflection is considered a vital constituent of reflective learning and reflective practice.",
    "5 Reflective practice enables the development of critical thinking skills, self-awareness, and continuous improvement."
  ],
